column1:
Wow, look, [1B]S1! The lights are
SO pretty!

Mewheheheh, the night sky may be beautiful,
but you are even more dazzling, Lady Ann...!

Oh, I can see the tower by Odori Park! Look,
look! It's so shiny!

Man, I had no idea there was a Ferris wheel
right in the middle of the city like this!
I wish it was just the two of us...
Sorry I'm being a third wheel.
Huh!? Oh, well isn't that sweet?
Oh, you meant the view... Eheheh...
Mrow!? You sayin' I'm a third wheel!?

Ahahaha, he's just kidding around! No need to
pout like that.

Nyahahaha, don't sweat it! You've done great
bringing me here— I mean, bringing us here!

...Still, it feels so strange to be here in Sapporo
like this.

I do travel a lot for the photoshoots, and it's
been both an eye-opener and a blast...

But the time I spend with all you guys is what's
really special to me. This trip's made that extra
clear to me.

Having all of you in my corner makes it easy
for me to keep pushing myself. So... thanks.

It's time I return the favor and start helping
others instead of always depending on them.
You help us all the time.

You think so? I'd love it if I really did manage to
pull it off.
Really? Then I oughta keep it up!
I hafta say, hearing that from you is a big relief, [1B]S1.

I'm thinking about going and seeing Alice when
we get back to Tokyo.

I mean, I did promise to be her friend and all—
I should be there for her while she works on
her comeback.

Oh, but the real-world Alice won't remember
any of that...
I'm sure you got through to her.
Yeah, I bet I'll be able to reach her somehow.

Don't you worry, Lady Ann. I'm sure the two of
you'll hit it off just fine!
Thanks! I'll give it my best!

We enjoyed the Sapporo
evening view together...

I feel like my bond with
Ann has grown stronger...
